reviews.review_text:
The Weight This seems like a good night 
for Brent;
Vocals are strong and keys driven.
Signs of being One Toke over the line..
and Bobby;
4 Weir tunes in a row
Including rare Truckin-) Smokestack
In hindsight Garcia good on guitar
but vocally winded at times.
The Weight was a perfect tune 
for the boys
everybody grabs a verse.
Very effective as an encore.
This was a good run
but not as snuggly
as Deer Creek
and not as epic
as Soldier Field
First and last appearance
At Tinley Park
Death Don’t
Have
No Mercy

P.S -in memory of Ozzy Osbourne 🦇2025
